reviewText: Not a lot of process control, and you really need the NScope to get a functional understanding of this stuff, but Nscope is no longer sold. those videos should be updated with a product that is less likely to go away.

Great course, great content and learning material. It has real lab exercises with careful instructions. You can still do the assignment without real circuit, but learning by doing will be more efficient, and of course this subject needs real equipment.The quiz is really helpful for each module lesson, but some of them are a bit difficult or having typing problem. Teachers should acknowledge and correct that. I hope lecture videos can have more animations about how devices work.
